com.complexible.common.openrdf.model

Class ContextAwareValueFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.complexible.common.openrdf.model.ContextAwareValueFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openrdf.model.ValueFactory

    public final class ContextAwareValueFactory
extends Object
implements org.openrdf.model.ValueFactory

    ValueFactory implementation which will create statements of the type ContextAwareStatement, otherwise it delegates creation of objects to the default ValueFactory

    Since:
    0.4.1
